						               													<description>Welcome to the tournament of the best voices of fairy kingdoms! Here you will become minstrels composing songs about precedented and unprecedented feats of heroes &amp;mdash; be it noble robbers, wise wizards, greedy dragons, valiant knights or beautiful princesses!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#208;&amp;#156;&amp;#208;&amp;#181;&amp;#208;&amp;#189;&amp;#208;&amp;#181;&amp;#209;&amp;#129;&amp;#209;&amp;#130;&amp;#209;&amp;#128;&amp;#208;&amp;#181;&amp;#208;&amp;#187;&amp;#208;&amp;#184; (Minstrels) is a roll-and-place game. Each player receives his own game board, on which he will place wooden figures of heroes and combine them. Gameplay is fast and simple: each round 2 dice are rolled and two numbers are shown, which simultaneously corresponds a place on game board where a figure of hero can be placed, and the type of a figure. Starting with the first player, all players take turns and choose individually for himself which one die will indicate the place on game board, and which die will indicate the figure of hero. In addition, a player can change numbers on dices individually for himself by paying coins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Adapt to rolled result or change it with coins and collect the most profitable combinations, because correct arrangement of heroes in rows, columns, and cells corresponding to the quest card will bring you victory points! Player who gain most points will be winner and earn the title of the most talented minstrel who sang the best song!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
